 Phillips at Palm Springs Film Festival|last=Harris|first=Latesha|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=December 10, 2019|accessdate=December 13, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213150033/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/todd-phillips-joker-creative-impact-directing-award-1203431581/|archive-date=December 13, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| Creative Impact in Directing Award\n| Todd Phillips\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals|PETA Oscats]]\n| January 28, 2020\n| Best Actor\n| Joaquin Phoenix\n| {{Won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.peta.org/blog/peta-oscats-2019s-best-films-stars-animals/|title=The Results Are In: Meet 2019\u2019s PETA Oscat Winners|last=Englar|first=Carolyn|website=[[People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals]]|date=January 28, 2020|accessdate=February 3, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201072617/https://www.peta.org/blog/peta-oscats-2019s-best-films-stars-animals/|archive-date=February 1, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Producers Guild of America Awards]]\n| [[Producers Guild of America Awards 2019|January 18, 2020]]\n| [[Producers Guild of America Award for Best Theatrical Motion Picture|Best Theatrical Motion Picture]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" |''Joker''\n| {{Nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/pga-awards-winners-2020-1203471639/|title=PGA Awards Winners: Complete List|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|first=Adam|last=B. Vary|date=January 18, 2020|accessdate=January 19, 2020}}</ref><br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/producers-guild-awards-2020-winners-list-full-1269972/item/outstanding-producer-animated-theatrical-motion-pictures-1269978|title=PGA Awards: '1917' Named Outstanding Motion Picture|last=Crist|first=Allison|website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=January 18, 2020|accessdate=January 19, 2020}}</ref>\