, 2019|accessdate=October 9, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204040405/https://variety.com/2019/music/news/society-composers-lyricists-awards-nominations-hildur-gudnadottir-1203423846/|archive-date=December 4, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Turkish Film Critics Association]]\n| January 7, 2020\n| Best Foreign Film\n| ''Joker''\n| {{draw|5th Place}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bianet.org/english/art/218195-film-critics-association-names-parasite-the-best-foreign-film-of-2019|title=Film Critics Association Names \u2018Parasite\u2019 the Best Foreign Film of 2019|last=|first=|website=bianet.org|date=January 7, 2020|accessdate=January 7, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314001950/http://bianet.org/english/art/218195-film-critics-association-names-parasite-the-best-foreign-film-of-2019|archive-date=March 14, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Vancouver Film Critics Circle]]\n| December 16, 2019\n| [[Vancouver Film Critics Circle Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n| Joaquin Phoenix\n| {{Nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2019/12/13/2020-nominees-announced/|title=2020 Nominees Announced|last=Cabrita|first=Josh|website=[[Vancouver Film Critics Circle]]|date=December 13, 2019|accessdate=December 13, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213184104/https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2019/12/13/2020-nominees-announced/|archive-date=December 13, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2019/12/16/parasite-named-best-picture-of-2019-by-vfcc/|title=Parasite Named Best Picture by VFCC|last=Cabrita|first=Josh|website=[[Vancouver Film Critics Circle]]|date=December 16, 2019|accessdate=December 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" scope=\"row\"| [[Venice Film Festival]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[76th Venice International Film Festival|September 7, 2019]]\n| [[Golden Lion]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |''Joker''\n| {{Won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"3\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/venice-film-festival-awards-revealed-1237684|title=Venice: Todd Phillips' 'Joker' Wins Golden Lion, Roman Polanski Wins Silver Lion|last=Anderson|first=Ariston|website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=September 6, 2019|accessdate=November 22, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190907190057/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/venice-film-festival-awards-revealed-1237684|archive-date=September 7, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.labiennale.org/en/news/collateral-awards-76th-venice-film-festival|title=COLLATERAL AWARDS OF THE 76TH VENICE FILM FESTIVAL|last=Venice Biennale Editors|website=[[Venice Biennale]]|date=September 6, 2019|accessdate=November 22, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190907172648/https://www.labiennale.org/en/news/collateral-awards-76th-venice-film-festival|archive-date=September 7, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| Graffetta d'Oro\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Premio Soundtrack Stars Award\n| Hildur Gu\u00f0nad\u00f3ttir\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Visual Effects Society]]\n| [[18th Visual Effects Society Awards|January 29, 2020]]\n| [[Visual Effects Society Award for Outstanding Supporting Visual Effects in a Feature Motion Picture|Outstanding Supporting Visual Effects in a Photoreal Feature]]\n| Edwin Rivera, Brice Parker, Mathew Giampa, Bryan Godwin, Jeff Brink\n| {{Nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2020-visual-effects-society-awards-nominations-full-list-1265672/item/outstanding-visual-effects-a-photoreal-feature-1265776|title=Baby Yoda, Alita, Simba Among VFX Society Awards Nominees|last=Giardina|first=Carolyn|website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=January 7, 2020|accessdate=January 7, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114070710/https://www.hollywoodreporter.